title: VA - Cities' Sampler Vol. 7 Essentials (1995) [FLAC]
description:
VA - Cities' Sampler Vol. 7 Essentials (1995)

From KTCZ 97.1 FM in Minneapolis, MN. U.S.A

'unique live performances and previously unavailable tracks make Vol. 7 an essential part of your music collection'.

01 Little Feat - Romance Without Finance
02 Freedy Johnston - Bad Reputation
03 Dave Matthews Band - Ants Marching
04 Shawn Colvin - Window To The World
05 Martin Zellar - East Side Boys
06 Sonny Landreth - South Of I-10
07 Paula Cole - Happy Home
08 Billy Pilgrim - Sweet Louisiana Sound
09 Todd Snider - Alright Guy
10 Jayhawks - Waiting For The Sun
11 Tina And The B-Side Movement - Paper Doll
12 Big Mountain - Fruitful Days
13 James McMurtry - Melinda

I use to travel to Minneapolis several times every year and my first stop everytime was the local music shop to pick up these great collections. I have several more I have collected over the years but this is, by far, my favorite one in this series
